product.Name: AI-Powered Health Data Masking
product.ShortDescription: The AI-Powered Health Data Masking solution helps healthcare organizations identify and mask health data in images or text. This solution uses Amazon Comprehend Medical to detect health data in a body of text, Amazon Rekognition to identify text in an image, Amazon API Gateway and AWS Lambda to provide an API interface for this functionality, and AWS Identity and Access Management (IAM) to authorize API requests.
